Title: Bagpipes Blackwood Chanter - Shepherd
long_description: The Shepherd Pipe Chanter - The Shepherd Blackwood Pipe chanter is one of the most popular chanters on the market today. It has been consistently used by some of the worlds best pipe bands for many years. The chanter has a well balanced scale, and good volume. The chanter is easy to reed and works best with the Shepherd or Ross pipe chanter reeds. The chanter usually pitches between 476 Hz and 479 Hz. A good pipe chanter is the most important part of the bagpipe, so it is important to get the co

Title: Bagpipes Blackwood Chanter - Dunbar
long_description: The Dunbar Pipe Chanter Blackwood - The Dunbar Blackwood Pipe Chanter is a good pipe chanter and well balanced across all notes. The chanter usually pitches between 478 Hz and 482 Hz. A good pipe chanter is the most important part of the bagpipe, so it is important to get the correct one for your needs.

Title: Bagpipes Poly Chanter - G1
long_description: The G1 Platinum Chanter has been designed and crafted to provide the highest quality sound with optimum comfortability. The chanter easily reaches the demands of the modern day pitch, stability and tonal quality without having oversized holes.

Title: Bagpipes Blackwood Chanter - McCallum McC2
long_description: McCallum McC2 Balckwood Pipe Chanter - The McCallum McC2 Pipe Chanter has fast become one of the more popular choices for solo pipers. The chanter was designed with the help of Willie McCallum. The chanter is easy to reed and takes a wide variety of reeds. This chanter pitches a bit lower than normal band chanters. It usually comes in at around chanter usually pitches between 473 Hz and 476 Hz. Each McC2 chanter is tested by Willie McCallum before it is sent out to the customer.

Title: Bagpipes Poly Chanter - McCallum

Title: Bagpipe Maintenance - Rehemp
long_description:
Rehemping of a tuning pin, or stock.

Price includes labour and materials.

Title: Bagpipe Maintenance - Bag
long_description:
The bags of the bagpipes require some regular maintenance.  A synthetic bag needs to have joints checked, moisture control checked.  Leather bags need to be seasoned, have joints checked.

Bag maintenance is billed per hour.

Title: Elliot Chanter Reed (Weak)
long_description: Elliot Pipe Chanter Reed - The Elliot Pipe chanter reed is a good stable reed for all levels of player. This reed has been used in both band and solo competitions. Having a good quality bagpipe chanter reed is very important when playing a bagpipe.

Title: Reed - Walsh Practice Chanter
long_description: The Walsh practice chanter reed is one of the best selling practice reeds that we carry. It fits well in pretty much any chanter. It take a medium air flow, and provides good volume. Having a good sounding practice chanter reed is very important for playing a practice chanter. All of our practice chanter reeds are all pre-tested before shipping. They are packaged individually in a plastic reed pack to protect them when not in use. Such a stylish way to show off your Irish/Scottish pride! Great functioning purse with a cell phone pocket inside and key rings too.

This Red Plaid kilt purse is pleated in the back to look like a kilt.  This Red Plaid is a very tradition tartan.

The outside Sporran functions as a coin purse too.
